{
  "stem": "8233.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still think I did see my-- it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could not forgive myself for not have seen her before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I went back and my mother came from work, because she had gone to work, I put on a face.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told my mother that my sister went to another camp, that they took care of her, that my friend made it all possible.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she went to another camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I don't know if my mother believed me or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CRYING] [SOBBING] Another time, when we worked together with my mother, somebody that was already-- we worked indoors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We worked in a Weberei, where we were making supplies for soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- we made long strips of some kind of rubber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said it was for tanks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to deliver that much every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But with the time, some of our friends find a way to mark it-- you know, and to take off the mark, so we wouldn't be punished that we didn't make that much that day.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS] My mother had made another kind of work in the same barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] One day, a man came in from the men's-- because they would, would go-- bringing in materials for us to work.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That man always used to call me, bring a little something for us from that friend that I found.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It would be a little bit of sugar, sometimes a little bit of margarine or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I would share with my friend next to me and my mother, of course.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day he came very happy, the same man.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your father is alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your father came from Jaworzno to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you shouldn't worry.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
